ola, suggest that we are entering a new phase in human evolutionary history-one that makes the future less predictable and more interesting than ever before.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Apr 2020) 0aHuman evolution. 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Evolution.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300224504423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300224504.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO